Author: clickgem
Title: [ANN][PRIVATE SALE] CLICKGEM (CGM & CGMT) – THE GLOBAL PAYMENT REVOLUTION !!!
Body: BEWARE WITH PHISHING WEBSITES, PHISHING EMAILS, PHISHING PROGRAMS AND DIRTY MARKETING!  Hello all members,  1. Some people are complaining that someone logged into their account and send CGM to other wallets! » We have done an investigation into our system and found no error to create that problem. The ratio of accounts have this problem is very small (100 of 60000). So we are thinking that these people are victims of phishing websites, phishing emails, phishing programs or keylogger software. To secure your account, please: - Enable Two Factor Authentication on your account (at backend menu, in section My account » Profile & Secures) - Install an Antivirus software on your computer to protect you from keylogger software. - Only read our news, our updates and follow marketing programs (airdrop & bounty) from our official website (https://www.clickgem.com/news.html) and our official Telegram channel (https://t.me/clickgem) ** We refuse all responsibilities to members who become victims of hackers!  2. Some people are sending this link https://thehackingteam.com/clickgem-cgm-ico-review/ to us and questioning us about the contents of that article! » If you spent a little time to read all contents written in that article, you will see it isn't a serious review! They write very general, haven't any proofs and have many ads on their page... They wrote this article before our ICO (at that time we have not yet created any application, only mentioned in the whitepaper and the roadmap). Also, we saw they wrote like that about a lot of ICO projects. Maybe because we spent a lot of money for ICO marketing and got a lot of visitors within a short time, so we think they just write like that about our project to attract visitors from our project to their website and earn money from ads on that page. That is just a dirty marketing trick! Our team has tried to contact the administrator of that website to remove that article, but they ignore and no answer! Until now, we don't scam money from any people. Although we failed with the ICO and the money we got from the ICO is even a lot less than the money we spent for ICO marketing companies, but we didn't give up and still continue this project. We are spending ourselves money to continue this project! We only think that we are creating useful applications for people and only hope they will welcome and use our applications so we can start earning fees from these applications! Have no reason to say we are scamming people or we are a scam project!  #ClickGem #CGM #CryptoCurrency #BlockChain #BewarePhishingWesbites #BewarePhishingEmails #BewarePhishingPrograms #BewareKeyloggerSoftware #BewareDirtyMarketing

So blockchain platform and cryptocurrency are not their main applications, their blockchain platform and cryptocurrency are developed from open source of Litecoin and both of them are only part of this project. They only release cryptocurrency (ICO) as a way to raise more funds from the community (crowdfunding) to help them develop project better!  Second, we want to confirm that we are just media representative of ClickGem project, no admin in this Telegram channel is coming from the ClickGem team member! As informed in our previous post, team members of ClickGem are only having two main people at this time are a professional programmer and his sponsor. The ClickGem team are really hard working at this time to focus to complete on developing their main application is a payment system (paygate) which will be launched on the Shanghai blockchain event. This is their only opportunity to prove to people that they are the real working project and their application is really useful for every people, also continue finding more funding sources for their project from this event. Can be considered as a survival opportunity for this project! Flight ticket, hotel room and a booth at the exhibition are already reserved. The brand identity and accompanying materials are also in the printing process. So, for sure, they will attend to this Shanghai event!  Third, because of two reasons in above, they will not continue to list their cryptocurrency (CGM) on other exchanges before when they launched their main application. Listed CGM on LocalBitcoinCash is just a test for the market. The ClickGem project has just started, main application and other applications are still in developing progress. The ClickGem team know that no one will buy CGM at this time even if it is listed on big exchanges because people will wait to see the potential of ClickGem project before taking their decision to invest in CGM and they can only see the potential of this project when its main application is launched! So, listing CGM to other exchanges at this time is only waste time and money, those exchanges will stop listing CGM after a short time if no one buys it... This time is very early to sell CGM! Any of your efforts to sell CGM with low price at this time is only reduce the value of ClickGem project and making the efforts of the ClickGem team become worthless, also people who have spent money to invest in this project will be put in a difficult situation! PLEASE HOLD AND NEVER SELL WITH LOW PRICE!!!  The ClickGem team really need and always need more trust and more support from the community to get more motivation to implement and develop the project, bringing it to the peak of success!  Please do not continue to spread information that is detrimental to this project! Please do not continue to ask questions like "How to sell CGM?", "Why can not sell CGM?" or something like that at this time!!! If you do not believe this project or do not have enough patience to follow it, just unsubscribe from ClickGem's community and delete this project from your mind! Body: Yep, I didn't give my opinion in that reply because I wanted to deliver just the result of my research and make anyone use those info to have a point of view, but lots of people didn't read research carefully and they saw that as big prove that this ICO is legit (over-reacted).  If you read that document, you find that the company has been opened to do normal business and not ICOs ! they didn't define the type of business that the company does, but they mentioned the company shouldn't do any business that is not legal in Belize. Second things, it's like a virtual company, there is no real office, it opened through internet, but it's still a company under the law of belize although we can not know who the owner which is not good ( $640 is just money to open the company for you, it requires adding specific amount in your bank account that open for you in Belize).  Through that research, we only know that Certificate of incorporation that they provided is real, we find out how they created the company and that the authorized share capital of Clickgem company is $50,000, also we found answer to our previous question, why the guy they mentioned in the post on telegram is from Vietnam and the company is in Belize.  Back to question : Is this project legit or not?  For me it's not only about legit and scam, it's also about knowing if the project is good business or bad in order to invest or not. Therefore, I still think that revealing the team members identity is required for this type of business, we need to know if they can deliver the products and implement the roadmap, plus they need to deliver quality product and not creating a joke and called it exchange then asking people to trade ! I when read the roadmap then log in to the platform, I feel there is no hope to see anything of those stuff in future. There is big gap between what we see in the roadmap of services that requires lots of money and big team, lawyer to achieve and the website

PANAMA -  Do you realize something? If project is not successful, they do not need to stand by their words and promises, they close the website and it's done. 2. You can not identify the real owner of the company 3. Body: WE ARE PART OF THE GLOBAL PAYMENT REVOLUTION   WWW.CLICKGEM.COM – WHITEPAPER – ROADMAP – LEGAL DOCUMENTS – NEWS – EVENTS – FAQ – API – TELEGRAM CHANNEL – TELEGRAM COMMUNITY    EVENTS WE PARTICIPATE IN     ON THE PRESS     CERTIFICATE & AWARD     PROJECT SUMMARY  As planned, ClickGem Project will run an ICO private sale and then soon after, a public sale on qryptos.com, which is currently ranked #50-60 on CoinMarketCap and part of Quoine - a top Japanese exchange. The benefit of joining the private sale is that investors have the opportunity to be among the first to own the tokens with a bonus up to 95% of the purchased tokens, that is similar with a discount up to 50% of selling price. As you probably know, once the ICO public sale is running, the benefit will be reduced and make the selling price tend to shoot up. This is a once in a lifetime opportunity for the investors who believe in ClickGem Project as the new way of doing transactions online. We are also guaranteed the listing on qryptos.com and liquid.com (Quoine’s new strategic exchange) after ICO. MOU signed with Quoine: https://www.clickgem.com/uploads/news/QUOINE-ClickGem-MOU.pdf  Another good news is that the Clickgem team is continuously expanding and was recently joined by Liam Robertson, CEO of Alphabit Fund - one of the world largest crypto hedge funds with capital size over 500 million U.S. Dollars. http://www.nbc12.com/story/38741552/one-of-the-biggest-names-in-blockchain-joins-clickgem-project-as-team-advisor (Press release about this event have also published on over 50 other press/media channels)  On 6th June 2018, the ClickGem Project attended the ICORace in Switzerland. Over 140 ICO projects from multiple different countries competed in the ICORace and ClickGem was one of the 24 projects that reached to the semifinals. https://www.clickgem.com/updates-jul-24-2018-clickgem-recived-official-certificate-from-icorace-2018-switzerland.html https://icorace.ch/winners/  Currently, ClickGem has a community with over 80,000 registered users (over 40,000 followers on social channels). The platform is already fully operational with all basic features running smoothly. Meanwhile, technicians are developing advanced features which will further improve the security and stability of the system. Using its current API, the platform integrates with all e-commerce platforms: https://api.clickgem.com/paygate/  You can find more information about our project and our ICO on our website (www.clickgem.com)    WHAT IS CLICKGEM PROJECT?  ClickGem Project is part of the global payment revolution!  ClickGem project is developing a complex ecosystem for all fiat currencies and cryptocurrencies. All of us agree that cryptocurrencies can't replace fiat currencies, at least at this time. For example: a merchant can receive payment via cryptocurrencies but they still need fiat currencies for paying their costs (labors, manufacture system, supply chains, activity expenses, government taxes, etc...) and they will worry a lot, really worry about the exchange rate of cryptocurrencies because they are not stable at all. However, if we can find a way to combine and operate cryptocurrency and fiat currency in a smart way, it will solve many of the above problems! And ClickGem is a solution: merchant still sells their products in a specified fiat currency while ClickGem paygate will support all buyers that can pay by any fiat currency or even cryptocurrency. ClickGem paygate will exchange currency of the payment through P2P currency exchange market into currency specified by the merchant before it comes to their hand, so they will never worry about the exchange rate of fiat currencies and cryptocurrencies. The payment at that time really has no border.  The ClickGem Project is a new groundbreaking and frictionless payment system. Our aim is creating a cross-border payment solution solves all the issues of current payment methods, that will surpass all other payment systems, including PayPal, Visa, etc… And help purchases easier, simpler, instantly with minimal cost.  We are the pioneers in developing a new payment gateway (paygate) which can support the pay-and-receive payment process with multiple currencies, including cryptocurrencies, support exchanging currency instantly with the lowest exchange rate from the market and just 0.1% transaction fee.  The ClickGem Project is designed as an open platform to facilitate the process of purchases by integrating and supporting transactions between most major fiat currencies and all cryptocurrencies through APIs. Minor fiat currencies and cryptocurrencies will be continually added in the future.  The team is continuously developing new APIs for the platform, f.ex. to integrate ClickGem exchange system with other external exchanges to optimize liquidity when exchanging currencies for the payment, apart from the already existing API which allows for integration with all today's e-commerce platforms, all B2B/B2C platforms, all applications for accepting payments online, and any software for collecting payments at local stores, supermarkets, etc...  With this idea, ClickGem can collaborate with all kinds of businesses, all service providers to build ClickGem’s ecosystem and its network to any place, access all markets in the world. This is how ClickGem will grow very fast and its scalability is unlimited.  ClickGem core application is a combination of: ❖ A multi-currency digital wallet which can store almost of currencies includes Fiat currencies such as USD, EUR, etc... and cryptocurrencies such as BTC, ETH, CGM, etc... ❖ A mix-exchange platform is the combination of a cryptocurrency exchange with a Fiat currency exchange (traditional currency exchange / Forex): it can support to exchange cryptocurrency to cryptocurrency, Fiat currency - Fiat currency, and cross-exchange cryptocurrency - Fiat currency (and vice versa). ❖ A Paygate (payment gateway) which closely integrated with the multi-currency digital wallet and mix-exchange platform, this combined system can process both payment transaction and currency exchange at the same time. This combined system can also support to pay and receive payment with most of currencies around the world including fiat currencies (such as USD, EUR, etc…) and cryptocurrencies (such as BTC, ETH, CGM, etc…): Sellers can designate any fixed currency they wish to receive while buyers can pay with any currency they having in their multi-currency wallet; Using ClickGem cryptocurrency (CGM) for payment will incur fewer fees than other currencies!  To understand more fully about how ClickGem system work, please watch our slideshow presentation at here: https://www.clickgem.com/presentation.html  View Detail Solutions | View Presentation | Experience The Paygate | API & e-Commerce Plugins    WHAT IS CLICKGEM ECOSYSTEM?  • Business Apps: B2B, B2C, Accept payment online • Banking Apps: Money transfer, saving program. • Entertainment Apps: Lotto, Sports betting, Web games and Mobile games • Utility/Service Apps: Transport booking, Hotel booking, etc… • Mobile App: With your smartphone, you just need to download the ClickGem mobile apps, and then you can start transferring money and making any payment with your clients, your partners, your suppliers... By using the ClickGem apps, there’s no need to fill out tons of annoying forms which is oppressively complex and time-consuming and may result in delays in getting business done. • Debit Card: Using the Debit Card of ClickGem is the simplest and most convenient way to make your payments, and otherwise conduct any money transaction. We, with our partners, will provide you with a Debit Card that you can use anywhere, at any time, all over the world. You can also use it to withdraw or transfer money via an ATM machine.    CLICKGEM PROGRAMS (MVP)  CGWALLET | CGEXCHANGE | CGPAY | CGM & CGMT | CGCASINO | PARTNERSHIP | AFFILIATE   ROADMAP    INITIAL COIN OFFERING (ICO)  The ICO is a way to raise funds for ClickGem Project. The funds raised during this period will be used for building and developing our core Team, the Ecosystem for our apps, and running marketing campaigns, such that ClickGem’s brand awareness and reputation can be successfully built.  For investors, this is a great opportunity to get the privilege of being business co- founders. Our management team has commited to follow the roadmap to increase the value of ClickGem and promote it to be the leading cryptocurrency in the global market. The sooner investors buy ClickGem, the higher the earning potentials they will gain, both in the short term and long term. In the short term, the price would increase rapidly right after the ICO. You could earn money through Trading or Mining programs.  There are several ways to earn profit with ClickGem. Buying ICO coins at the best price enables you to optimize your investment. Therefore, you should not miss any of the latest information about the ICO calendar, so that you can be among the first individuals who could buy the coin at the best possible price.
